name: ALL HOLOGRAPHIC & RARE Pokemon Holo Grab Bag Lot 25 Card+BONUS! EX? GOLD STAR? CHARIZARD?
description:
This is the BEST Value Pokemon Card Grab Bag Lot ANYWHERE!

Other lots will promise to give you 1 holographic card and a rare or two, but the rest of their lots include a bunch of unwanted common and uncommon cards. What kid would want those??? Everyone knows that kids want to have the best, brightest, and most powerful cards after all! 

That's what my lot will give you.

Here is what other lots will offer you:

50 cards:

1 Holographic or Rare (No guarantee of a holo)

49 Uncommon and Common Cards

Here is the breakdown of MY lot:

25 cards +1 Bonus:

10 Holographics:

 - 3 Rare Holo

 - 3 Reverse Holo Rare

 - 4 Reverse Holo Un/Common 

15 Rares

1 Bonus Card (PROMO, EXTRA HOLO, OR AN ULTRA RARE CARD)

The cards in these lots can contain cards from EVERY set from Base-the most current set available so any collection will get a great jumpstart! 

You could even get...a CHARIZARD!

All of these cards are 100% authentic and in great condition (Usually near mint-mint).

ULTRA RARE CARDS INCLUDE:

EX, SHINING, GOLD STAR, 1ST EDITION OR EVEN A CHARIZARD EX OR RAYQUAZA *!!!



(The cards in the pictures may not be the cards that you will receive)
